# Rating #
Method for commenting on restaurants, menu items, and pictures. Append `/comment` to the locator of the resource to be commented upon.

## Request ##

**URL:** `http://example.com/restaurant/id/comment`  
**Format:** JSON  
**Method:** PUT  
**Requires Authentication:** Yes  
**Parameters:**  
