## Response ##

### Success ###

**Format:** JSON  
**Status Code:** 201  
**Sample data:**

> {"status": "created"}

### Failure ###

**Format:** JSON  
**Status Code:** 422  
**Sample data:**

> {"status": "unprocessable_entry"}
